extendedInfo.description: JAFF MILITARY WORKOUT TRAINER!+ Awesome full body workout program! + 60 workout days with individual training plans for each day!+ 20+ different exercises for efficient full body training!+ All features included, no in-app purchases necessary!+ Made for all those who need strength and endurance every day - whether in the military, for their job or in private life!GAIN STRENGTH AND ENDURANCE!+ Use your own body weight as resistance!+ No gym or additional equipment required! + Exercises can be performed at any place around the world!+ Perfect workout whenever there is no gym around the corner!START NOW!+ Get in shape and see results! JAFF gives you a carefully composed workout for every day.+ Improve balance, flexibility and strength! Arms, chest, abs, core, legs - all major muscle groups are covered.+ Stay motivated! Every exercise is supported by an animated timer counting your repetitions.+ Control your achievements! Check your stats and see how much you achieved since starting your workout program.------------------------+ JAFF Military Workout Trainer contains the same great workout programm as JAFF Home Workout, also available for Android. It provides a new, professional layout and sets fresh motivations.

reviews.comment: I needed a new set to shock my body. Awesome app the first workout got the job done. Can not wait too try the rest of the workouts.

reviews.title: Nice for Beginners
reviews.comment: For the first 3 - 4 weeks the exercises were great for someone who was starting back into working out.  I wish the exercise descriptions were clearer on some and overall speed of the app was frustrating.  Think its time to move on after 2 months.

reviews.title: #1 app for fitness

I can feel pain in my shoulders. Definitely hard.  Settings scroll to set lower portion exercise not working for me due to low resolution. Please fix it, but all the exercise in this app rules out that issue. I will do squats and adjust for that.
